TI  - Depth estimation of pipe wall thinning using multifrequency reflection coefficients of T(0,1) mode-guided waves with supervised multilayer perceptron
T2  - STRUCTURAL HEALTH MONITORING-AN INTERNATIONAL JOURNAL
LA  - English
